"The user starts with View 1 (Overview) analyzing daily sales trends and campaign impacts through stacked area charts. By selecting time ranges on the x-axis brush, they filter data in View 2 (Exploration) showing inventory-sales relationships and View 3 (Exploration) examining delivery status impacts. The heatmap in View 4 (Insight) automatically updates to show weekly seasonal patterns within the selected time frame, with optional campaign overlays helping correlate marketing activities with revenue peaks."